* define this setting:
```json
"workbench.customColorTheme": {
    "extends": "Abyss",
    "type": "dark",
    "colors": {
        "statusBarItemActiveBackground": "#ff0000"
    }
}
```

=> does not work because statusBarItemActiveBackground is defined as CSS rule [here](https://github.com/Microsoft/vscode/blob/master/src/vs/workbench/browser/parts/statusbar/statusbarPart.ts#L322).
